  <body>
    <segment id="1">
But not with us!</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="31" relname="interpretation"> 

How naive can some school principals actually be?</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="2" relname="antithesis">  

&quot;Drugs? No problem at our school,&quot; you hear again and again.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="31" relname="span"> 

The police know better.</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="20" relname="concession"> 

And many principals know it too.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="20" relname="span"> 

But nothing should leak out because the number of students is falling and there is a threat of closure,</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="4" relname="circumstance"> 

if the school falls into disrepute.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="29" relname="span">

However, by remaining silent, one cannot make the problem go away.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="22" relname="span">  

Under the guise of looking away and concealment, the drug trade and consumption thrive even more undisturbed than,</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="21" relname="conjunction"> 

where everyone keeps their eyes open </segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="21" relname="conjunction"> 

and talks about the problem.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="23" relname="conjunction">

The enormous profit margins of the drug trade attract criminals,</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="23" relname="conjunction">

and the immense prices for illegal drugs force addicts to obtain the money through break-ins and robberies.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="30" relname="span">  

It is a shame, therefore, that the parents of the teenagers in the Temnitz district were so uninterested in the police&apos;s advice on Tuesday.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="26" relname="list">  

How a joint actually looks and smells,</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="25" relname="span"> 

what dilated pupils reveal,</segment>
    <segment id="17" parent="24" relname="span"> 

which also do not close,</segment>
    <segment id="18" parent="17" relname="circumstance"> 

even when shining a flashlight into the daughter&apos;s eye - </segment>
    <segment id="19" parent="27" relname="joint"> 

all this knowledge could open the eyes of some unsuspecting mother.
</segment>
<group id="20" type="span" parent="28" relname="span" />
